  $lang['TEAM_T'] = 'SoulFire Team'; 
  $lang['TEAM'] = 'The beginning of SoulFire team reach year 2005 when the redaction of now non-existing service World of Gothic PL decided to translate German and Russian modifications of Gothic games. Mod tools were released on August 2003 but because of 1,5 year delay of "the Night of the Raven" addon in Poland (and lack of access to Polish game scripts) fans were forced to wait. At the turn of 2005 and 2006 there were more and more foreign projects published (modding in Poland was still doing baby steps).. Team decided that this is a good moment to start popularization of mods and provide an extra entertainment to the fans of the game. First polish version published by us (3rd June 2006) was modification of VisiGothic. Between 2006 and 2009 we translated nine modifications to both parts of the game. At the end of 2008 the idea of creating our original project - "The History of Khorinis" - was born. Project in current form is under development since 2015. At present, our team gathers specialists and professionals from all fields - students and professional 2D and 3D graphic artists, designers, concept artists, composer, composers, writers and programmers. All of them share serious approach to their tasks and what is most important - their belief in the project and love of the game. Thanks to great work organization and already mentioned approach we can be proud of the highest level of work quality in the history of modding. Not only among fans of Gothic but also to the game itself. The grandness of our addon is to honor a great plot of the game and climate of its first titles as well as releasing product that stands at the level of the full-fledged part of the series.';
  $lang['TEAM_REC_T'] = 'Recruitment and contact';
